{
  "name": "Example baseline sortie mix",
  "category": "demo",
  "description": "Baseline scenario for quick smoke tests. Even mission split, moderate demand across MIR/SCAR/ES, and typical process times.",
  "questions": [
    "What is the expected throughput with baseline demand?",
    "Where are rejections likely to occur at current state counts?",
    "How sensitive are results to minor changes in process times?"
